<i>adjective</i>: 핸섬하다 [], 잘생기다 [잘생기다], 이쁘다 [이ː쁘다], 예쁘다 [예ː쁘다], 아리땁다 [아리땁따], 반반하다 [반반하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>핸섬하다 []</dt><br>
<dd>handsome; comely; good-looking</dd><br>
<dd>주로 남자가, 체격이 좋거나 얼굴이 깔끔하게 잘생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>Usually used for men, being well-built and having a neat and attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dt>잘생기다 [잘생기다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. good-looking; handsome; comely</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 얼굴 생김새가 훌륭하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a pleasing and attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>2. well-shaped; having good looks</dd><br>
<dd>모양이 번듯하여 보기에 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a good shape and therefore looking good.</dd><br>
<dt>이쁘다 [이ː쁘다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pretty; beautiful; comely</dd><br>
<dd>생긴 모양이 눈으로 보기에 좋을 만큼 아름답다.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance of someone or something looking good and beautiful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adorable</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 동작, 말투 등이 보기에 사랑스럽고 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior, movements, way of speaking, etc., being lovely and cute.</dd><br>
<dd>3. nice; good</dd><br>
<dd>아이가 행동이 바르고 말을 잘 들어서 흐뭇하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A child making one feel satisfied because he/she behaves correctly and does what he/she is told.</dd><br>
<dt>예쁘다 [예ː쁘다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pretty; beautiful; comely</dd><br>
<dd>생긴 모양이 눈으로 보기에 좋을 만큼 아름답다.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance of someone or something looking good and beautiful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adorable</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 동작, 말투 등이 보기에 사랑스럽고 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior, movements, way of speaking, etc., being lovely and cute.</dd><br>
<dd>3. nice; good</dd><br>
<dd>아이가 행동이 바르고 말을 잘 들어서 흐뭇하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A child making one feel satisfied because he/she behaves correctly and does what he/she is told.</dd><br>
<dt>아리땁다 [아리땁따]</dt><br>
<dd>lovely; beautiful; comely; sweet</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 행동, 모습 등이 예쁘고 곱다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's appearance being pretty or one's mind or behavior being gentle.</dd><br>
<dt>반반하다 [반반하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flat; level; even</dd><br>
<dd>표면이 구겨지거나 울퉁불퉁한 데가 없이 고르고 평평하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Smooth and flat without any rumples or bumps on the surface.</dd><br>
<dd>2. good-looking; comely; handsome</dd><br>
<dd>생김새가 예쁘거나 잘생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>Pretty or handsome in appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>3. decent; in good shape</dd><br>
<dd>물건 등이 겉으로 보기에도 좋고 쓸 만하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking good and usable as in goods, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>